      "rationale": "A three-level mesh refinement study (2.1 M, 5.8 M, and 14.2 M cells) was conducted at the nominal operating point. Richardson extrapolation yielded a GCI of 3.1% on the hemolysis index QoI. Achieved Gradation 2."
    },
