      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 2 for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Validation experiments used the same FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry and bovine blood analog fluid as the COU. Operating envelope of the validation activities fully spans the five COU flow-speed combinations. Achieved Gradation 2."
    },
