      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 2 for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "Iterative convergence was confirmed with residuals below 1e-5 for all equations and mass-flow imbalance below 0.01%. Sensitivity of NIH to tighter convergence criteria was less than 0.3%. Achieved Gradation 2."
    },
    {
