      "acceptanceCriteria": "Achieved level must meet or exceed required level of 2 for MRL 3.",
      "rationale": "The SST k-omega turbulence model with low-Reynolds-number correction was selected based on published benchmark comparisons for confined rotating flows. The Giersiepen power-law hemolysis model was used consistent with published FDA guidance. Achieved Gradation 2."
    },
