      "rationale": "Blood viscosity, density, and hemolysis model constants were taken from peer-reviewed literature with documented uncertainty ranges. A one-at-a-time sensitivity study confirmed NIH variation below 12% across the stated input uncertainty bands. Achieved Gradation 2."
